description:
Get ready for another mash up! On today’s episode, Emily is sharing some of the funniest, sexiest, and revealing conversations from comedians that she’s hosted over the past few years.

She talks with funny man Brad Williams, comedian Adam Ray, actor and author Fred Stoller, and Grace Para and Jen Bartels from the Lady Freaks, all of whom are sharing their funniest experiences in sex and relationships. From diffusing awkward situations – in the bedroom and the dating world – to epic threesomes, this show will have you laughing, and a little turned on.

Thank you for supporting our sponsors who help keep the show FREE: UVee, Womanizer, Intensity
